Notes
-----

This CVar is helpful in determining polycounts in a given scene, investigate compilation problems and the efficiency of visportals. See also the [R\_useScissor\_(cvar).html r\_useScissor] and [R\_showLightCount\_(cvar).html r\_showLightCount] CVars.


